00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,760
- Father! 
 - Father! Don't stop me!

17
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:35,460
I can't keep Zi Lin's secret anymore, Clan Leader!

18
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:40,120
What secret?

19
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:46,200
Since things have come to this point, I'll just tell you about it.

20
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:49,540
Zi Lin, you're not an ordinary tortoise.

21
00:01:49,540 --> 00:01:51,740
Zi Lin is an immortal tortoise from heaven.

22
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,720
The deceased Immortal Lord Bei Ming was his master.

23
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,880
He absorbed the essence of the sun and the moon.

24
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:59,160
So he's an divine tortoise.

25
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:01,900
I thought I was just an ordinary tortoise from a divine lake.

26
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:04,900
It turns out that my master was Immortal Lord Bei Ming?

27
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,260
- Really? 
 - Talk less.

28
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,440
This is Zi Lin's immortal form.

29
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,720
I thought my primordial pill just looked unique.

30
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,780
Turns out it was really precious.

31
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:22,240
Father-in-law, if you're willing to let Lin Lang marry me,

32
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:26,500
I'll gift her the immortal spirit for her to kick around like a ball if she wanted.

33
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:30,940
- Father. 
 - Even if you were an immortal cultivating in the heavenly realm,

34
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:33,420
you're still just a demon in the mortal world right now.

35
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:37,660
Our Fox Clan never has set up an alliance with the Tortoise Clan.

36
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:40,340
- If this goes public, how will I... 
 - Father! Father!

37
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:42,760
I don't care if he's a deity!

38
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:46,920
All I care about is if he loves me wholeheartedly.

39
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,800
Father, I beg you.

40
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,320
Promise me, okay?

41
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:52,500
Just fulfill our wishes, please?

42
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,640
- Father! 
 - I beg you.

43
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,120
- Please let us get married. 
 - I beg you too.

44
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,780
I don't want to leave the mountain.

45
00:02:56,780 --> 00:03:01,700
And I can't bear to leave the Mountain Chief and Sister Yan Dan.

46
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,380
Father...

47
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:18,080
Listen to me. The marriage must be held in the Mountain Chief Hall.

48
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:21,900
It must be filled with 88 tables. The food and drinks will constantly flow to show dignity.

49
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:24,940
- Father. 
 - Eighty-eight tables?

50
00:03:24,940 --> 00:03:27,080
We don't have that much money on the mountain.

51
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:30,400
Do it. Even if I lose everything, I'll still have to do it.

52
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:37,740
What's more, you have to ask a respected deity to be the witness.

53
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:41,360
- Well... 
 - Father!

54
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:43,860
Didn't you cultivate in the Heavenly Realm before?

55
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:46,360
Don't tell me you don't know any superior deities.

56
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:51,120
Clan Leader, if I may be so bold to ask, must it be a superior deity?

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,680
Yu Mo is the king of all demons.

58
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:55,580
- It'll be an honor to have him as their witness, right? 
  - Right! 

59
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:58,240
Or will an Earthly Deity do?

60
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,580
There's a Soil Guardian I know. He's really kind.

61
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:03,500
- Can you... 
 - No.

62
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,840
We're leaving!

63
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,360
- Find a superior deity. 
 - Father!

64
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,500
Only then can you come to the Fox Clan to propose!

65
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,760
- Father! Father. 
 - Clan Leader.

66
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,460
- Let's go. 
 - Father, calm down.

67
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:13,820
- Father. 
 - Clan Leader, please stop for a moment.

68
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:19,380
Mountain Chief Yu Mo. Please forgive me for being noisy and rude.

69
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:23,820
But Lin Lang is my most beloved daughter.

70
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:26,620
You treasure your daughter, I can understand that.

71
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:29,740
How hard could it be to find a superior deity as the witness?

72
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:33,820
An emperor who has descended to the Mortal Realm, would that satisfy you?

73
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,540
An emperor?

74
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:40,100
Lin Lang and Zi Lin got into trouble because of me.

75
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:44,060
I'll be the witness to their marriage, to bring them good luck.

76
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,780
Greetings, Your Majesty.

77
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:53,380
- I'm sorry for being rude. 
 - Father. What are you doing? Get up.

78
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:56,580
- He's our savior. He's Taoist Master Tang. 
 - Kneel down.

79
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:58,140
- All of you, kneel down. 
 - He captures demons.

80
00:04:58,140 --> 00:05:01,500
The Emperor is the savior of the Fox Clan.

81
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:04,580
During the War of Genesis, thanks to the Emperor's help,

82
00:05:04,580 --> 00:05:08,100
the Fox Clan managed to avoid the genocidal acts of the Asura Clan.

83
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:11,300
Back then, the Fox Clan avoided the war to survive.

84
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:16,400
After that, the Heavenly Court was going to denounce us and kicked the Fox Clan out of the Immortal Clan.

85
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:19,960
Our clan was bullied.

86
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:23,580
Because of your kindness, you saved the territories of the Fox Clan.

87
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:25,700
Which is how our clan was able to survive up to now.

88
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:29,260
Your portrait was kept in the ancestral temple of the Fox Clan this entire time.

89
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:34,920
Every clan leader is grateful for your kindness and we worship you.

90
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:40,620
I descended to the Mortal Realm to experience hardships.

91
00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:42,860
I can't remember the past.

92
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:48,640
If the kindness I did back then can bring a good outcome today, that is be a good thing.

93
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:51,520
As long as Lin Lang and Zi Lin love each other,

94
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:57,240
Yan Dan and I are willing to be witnesses to their marriage.

95
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:08,420
Father. I, Zi Lin, am more than willing.

96
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:12,300
If I can marry Lin Lang, I'll be sure to treasure her.

97
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:15,500
I'll love what she likes and hate what she hates.

98
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:21,340
Even if the world is torn apart and water flows backward, I'll never change my mind.

99
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:26,820
If I go back on my words, may I die a horrible death and never be able to reincarnate.

100
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,800
You're indeed a man.

101
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:32,320
I'll allow you two to get married.

102
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:43,100
Since Young Master Tang has such a noble status and he and the Fox Clan have such fate with each other,

103
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:47,760
then can these 88 tables of banqueting be...

104
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:56,480
Your Majesty. No. If Young Master Tang graces us with his presence as a witness to my daughter's marriage,

105
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:59,220
that would be a great honor for the Fox Clan.

106
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,540
How could I dare ask for anything more?

107
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:05,080
I'm willing to spare all the efforts of the Fox Clan,

108
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:09,980
and I'll offer the divine scriptures which have been passed down for tens of thousands of years to return the favor.

109
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:15,940
It's justified for Lin Lang to do anything for Yelan Mountain as a token of appreciation.

110
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:19,060
This is a predestined marriage.

111
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:22,240
A divine scripture that is tens of thousands of years old?

112
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:25,380
Let's do it! We have to hold this marriage now!

113
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:35,000
Can you take care of those split souls of yours?

114
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,440
They're wandering around all over.

115
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:40,640
If they were to come out at night, it would scare those timid demons.

116
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:45,640
I didn't see you when I woke up.

117
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:47,880
So I asked them to look for you.

118
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:50,200
And I happened to do this good deed.

119
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,980
How are you going to thank me?

120
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:56,140
I think the pleasant surprise is this box of divine scriptures.

121
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:59,140
I didn't expect the Leader of the Fox Clan to keep his promise.

122
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:03,160
He asked someone to bring this box of divine scriptures over so quickly.

123
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:09,900
I think that one of these books contains a spell to break that mysterious man's magic.

124
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:15,320
I think this Lotus Sutra is quite nice.

125
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:22,820
"It's suitable for those who suffer from internal deficiencies and a leaking of yang  (male)  force.."

126
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,980
This isn't suitable for you.

127
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,180
Why isn't it suitable for me? Let me see it.

128
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:33,280
I said it's not suitable, so it isn't.

129
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:37,000
Give... give it back to me!

130
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:44,340
"To cultivate this, the cultivator has to take off their clothing,"

131
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:48,280
"pick a person to inject the power into Dark Ice,"

132
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:51,740
"and wipe the whole body with Dark Ice."

133
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,240
I think it's quite suitable.

134
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,500
You vile man.

135
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,880
It's suitable for you, but not for me!

136
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,300
What are you doing?

137
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,940
You said that you wanted to save me.

138
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:11,920
How do you know it's not suitable without trying it?

139
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,400
I don't want to.

140
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:22,240
Isn't it written clearly in the book?

141
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,320
You're only going to wipe that one place?

142
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:36,900
Stop being too demanding, okay?

143
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,240
What about the neck?

144
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:07,780
It hurts.

145
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:12,580
- What's wrong? Are you shy? 
 - I'm not shy. I'm daring enough.

146
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:15,800
If so, why did you stop? Keep going.

147
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:22,220
My immortal spirit is hurting again.

148
00:10:22,220 --> 00:10:25,820
Since it hurts so much, why don't I help you with it.

149
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,760
Hei Tu, perfect timing.

150
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:30,420
- Hurry. Wipe it for him. 
 - Damn it.

151
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:36,100
Enough, you're severely injured, you should take care of yourself.

152
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:39,000
Besides, pretending to be sick to seek attention are all tricks I've used before.

153
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,300
It doesn't work at all.

154
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,700
It'll do as long as it works.

155
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:50,000
Since I'm dying, the most important thing is to be happy.

156
00:10:54,800 --> 00:11:00,300
Yan Dan, Zhao Lan's reply... I've put the letter in the Pavilion of Books.

157
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,300
Go read it if you have the time.

158
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,600
This palm is incurable, right?

159
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,300
How could it be?

160
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,400
There must be a way to cure it.

161
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,100
Didn't you hear Yu Mo just now?

162
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:18,900
Zhao Lan already wrote back to us. She must've figured it out.

163
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:21,800
You wait here. We'll come to you after discussing it.

164
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,000
You stay here in the water.

165
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,000
Yan Dan,

166
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:31,200
I've been in the mortal world for twenty years already.

167
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:34,000
Seems like I won't have a chance of getting married.

168
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:40,900
So, at Lin Lang and Zi Lin's wedding tomorrow, let's all be happy, okay?

169
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:45,300
What are you talking about? We're all happy.

170
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,000
I'm really happy too.

171
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:50,900
Besides, believe me. You won't die.

172
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:57,600
 Withered Stone Palm, as its name suggests, causes a stone-like occlusion in the person's meridian. 

173
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,800
 Medicine or magic aren't able to be injected into the body. 

174
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:04,600
 No matter how powerful the rescuer is, the power will still be thrown back by the body. 

175
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:07,400
 If the person who was hit has symptoms of pulse collision, 

176
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,800
 he'll die in ten days due to the inability of regulating the basis. 

177
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,800
 There's no cure for this palm. 

178
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:15,300
 I suggest you not to cast a spell recklessly. 

179
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:18,600
 Or it'll cause danger to yourself, causing you both to die. 

180
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:23,700
Yan Dan, eat something.

181
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:30,100
   

182
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,200
I found it.

183
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,200
Yu Mo, Yu Mo. I found it.

184
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:36,400
Look. In this Great Silk Scripture, there are 81 stances.

185
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:39,600
Every move and every stance is able to heal and prolong life.

186
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:42,300
We can save Tang Zhou now. I can save his life!

187
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:43,600
Yan Dan.

188
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,400
Zhao Lan already said it... this palm is incurable.

189
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:53,800
If you insist on using power to save him, the power will be thrown back into your body. It's useless.

190
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:56,400
What do we do then? I'm asking you what I should do now.

191
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:59,900
Should I just sit by and watch him die without doing anything?

192
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:05,900
I'm sorry.

193
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:10,300
I...

194
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,900
I didn't mean to lose my temper with you.

195
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:16,000
- I'm just... 
 - It's all right.

196
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,400
Yan Dan.

197
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:21,100
Tang Zhou is my blood-sworn brother.

198
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:24,400
I certainly want him to be alive and well.

199
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:29,700
I know. If Tang Zhou dies, you'll be heartbroken.

200
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:32,400
I've never expected you to give up on him.

201
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:37,400
I've already sent all the demon soldiers down the mountain to find the clues about the Ground Block.

202
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:42,100
Perhaps if they find it, then his power will be stabilized.

203
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:45,000
This is what Yelan Mountain owes Tang Zhou.

204
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,400
We'll naturally try our best to repay him.

205
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,100
For the time being,

206
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:54,200
he'll only be happy if you are.

207
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,400
Isn't that right?

208
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:02,000
Yu Mo, thank you.

209
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,400
Thanks.

210
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,400
You're running out of breath.

211
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,900
Yet, you still want to be a wedding officiant.

212
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:42,300
After the wedding ends, I can die without regrets.

213
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:47,500
After I die, you should go find a new master.

214
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:52,400
 If you die, there's no other master I can serve in this world. 

215
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:55,400
I have a qi-gathering method that might be worth trying.

216
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,600
It's useless.

217
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:03,100
Yan Dan and Yu Mo have gone through all the scriptures of the Divine Realm.

218
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:05,200
It's unsolvable.

219
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:08,000
Using qi-gathering methods is time-consuming.

220
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,100
Stop fussing around.

221
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:11,600
This method of mine is definitely different.

222
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:16,200
If you learn it, perhaps you can make it to tomorrow's wedding.

223
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,900
How about it? Do you want to learn it?

224
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:19,500
I won't learn demonic spells.

225
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:22,000
You're my sword master, how could I possibly harm you?

226
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,200
Come on, try it.

227
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,700
Forget all five senses.

228
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:33,800
Empty the six perceptions.

229
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:36,400
Reverse the mysteries.

230
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:07,800
 I'm cursed and I can't reveal your origin. 

231
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:12,500
 But I still made you learn your father's unique skill, Eternal Darkness. 

232
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:16,200
 As long as you can survive this, you'll achieve the same goal sooner or later. 

233
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:19,900
 We, the Asura Clan, can finally fulfill our wish as well. 

234
00:16:49,400 --> 00:16:51,600
 All of you, kneel down. 

235
00:16:55,800 --> 00:17:00,100
 Your Majesty, this is the last batch of slaves from the Quick Cypress Clan. 

236
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,500
 Congratulations, Your Majesty. 

237
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:07,100
 With the help of their spiritual power, it'll bring your Eternal Darkness to perfection. 

238
00:17:07,100 --> 00:17:10,300
 Ingesting the slaves can strengthen the cultivation base. 

